Job Responsibilities:

  Operates high tech equipment to ensure meeting production output with high yield and good quality
  Perform 1st level troubleshooting of any faults
  Perform basic maintenance and repairs jobs of equipment
  Assist Engineers to ensure proper process records are maintained
  Interface with other colleagues concerning quality and assure that effective corrective action or improvement is implemented
  Any other ad-hoc work as and when assigned


Requirements:&nbsp;

  ITE Certificate
  Entry level candidates with understanding in Electrical/ Engineering/ Electronic/ Optical Field
  Good team player with positive working attitude aad able to interact with all level
  Meticulous and careful in handling of delicate wafers
